params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the location that contains the entry groups to list. Can be provided as a URL.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of items to return. Default is 10. Maximum limit is 1000. Throws an invalid argument if page_size is greater than 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. Pagination token that specifies the next page to return. If empty, returns the first page.
